  <brief_title>Postoperative Desogestrel for Endometriosis Related Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Double Blind Randomized Controlled Trial to Study the Effectiveness of a Desogestrel for the Treatment of Pelvic Pain or Dysmenorrhea in the Patients Undergone Conservative Surgery for Pelvic Endometriosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
